init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United Nations is now involved in trying to figure out what exactly is going on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The following two weeks showed that the rankings were accurate.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This lead to an increase in divorce and social isolation for a lot of low ranking dads.
